==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stoker
<hw>Stok"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D. See
<er>Stoke</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos>]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who is
employed to tend a furnace and supply it with fuel, especially the
furnace of a locomotive or of a marine steam boiler; also, a machine for
feeding fuel to a fire.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A fire poker.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>C.
Richardson (Dict.).</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stokey</ent>⟦br⟧
